      "title": "Create OpenAI API key",
      "description": "## Create an OpenAI API key\n\n>If you haven't already, create an [OpenAI account](http://auth.openai.com/create-account).\n\n1. Sign into your OpenAI account at https://auth.openai.com/log-in.\n2. Visit https://platform.openai.com/api-keys\n3. Select the **Create new secret key** button.\n4. Select **Service account**.\n5. Name this key **Oktane lab**. Keep all other options as default.\n6. Select **Done**.\n\n> Your OpenAI API key is displayed in a pop up message. Keep this open for the next step.",
